- You don't say no to me

12:03.280 --> 12:05.253
in the middle of the pitch.

12:05.615 --> 12:06.754
I'm sold.

12:07.083 --> 12:08.263
Grocery bag.

12:11.054 --> 12:12.289
Hey, Chrissy.

12:12.622 --> 12:14.157
