14:00.263 --> 14:02.750
Big day today. Trevor's
first commercial shoot.

14:03.096 --> 14:04.467
Trevor!

14:04.501 --> 14:06.469
Let's go! Let's go, Trevor!

14:06.503 --> 14:08.917
Up, up! Wakey, wakey, let's go, pal...

14:10.120 --> 14:11.264
Damn it!

14:14.742 --> 14:15.796
Jizz.

14:16.226 --> 14:17.394
Fucking jizz.

14:23.124 --> 14:24.492
- Hey, Mom.
- Trevor told me

14:24.525 --> 14:26.561
- you were nasty to him.
- Why didn't he show up?

14:26.791 --> 14:28.826
Came crawling back to
you? Couldn't take it?

14:28.861 --> 14:30.829
You were supposed to show him the ropes!

14:30.863 --> 14:32.731
Not work him to death! He's a kid!

14:32.765 --> 14:34.271
He is not a kid, Mom!

14:34.400 --> 14:36.962
