17:48.643 --> 17:49.954
It was stupid, it was dumb.

17:50.057 --> 17:51.530
But you're so good at it.

17:51.840 --> 17:52.968
It's easy.

17:53.543 --> 17:55.244
It's your thing, man. It's not mine.

17:55.278 --> 17:56.395
What do you mean?

17:56.613 --> 17:57.914
Look, remember when we were kids

17:57.947 --> 17:59.994
and we would race and
you were faster than me,

18:00.019 --> 18:02.003
