18:28.875 --> 18:30.310
I didn't slow down.

18:30.343 --> 18:31.901
I just got tired.

18:49.896 --> 18:51.431
Mind if we join you guys?

18:51.740 --> 18:54.401
All my boys at the table together.

18:55.378 --> 18:57.303
Tim, you been crying?

18:57.722 --> 18:59.299
No, I'm just a little hot.

18:59.539 --> 19:01.739
